The Bull Has Sprung 2024 spring exhibit featuring Max Osiris is Atelier Osiris' 2nd exhibit. The first was Paris in Sept 2023. Since then Max has produced many artworks on different platforms, most frequently Superrare, where he was initially banned twice. 

This exhibit showcases his Superrare works in mostly chronological order from July '23 to now, and sees Max experiment more with AI.

Due to the abundant vertical real-estate enjoyed by Atelier Osiris, Max's artworks have been arranged in clusters. Text instructions provide direction guidance.

Tap or click each artwork for it's specific information and marketplace status.
